  <entry>
    <title>Laravel使用JWT</title>
    <link href="/2021/10/28/Laravel%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8JWT/"/>
    <url>/2021/10/28/Laravel%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8JWT/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Laravel-使用-JWT-做权限认证"><a href="#Laravel-使用-JWT-做权限认证" class="headerlink" title="Laravel 使用 JWT 做权限认证"></a>Laravel 使用 JWT 做权限认证</h1><h2 id="介绍"><a href="#介绍" class="headerlink" title="介绍"></a>介绍</h2><p><a href="https://jwt.io/">JWT</a>是 JSON Web Token 的缩写，是一个非常轻巧的规范，这个规范允许我们使用 JWT 在用户和服务器之间传递安全可靠的信息。<br>JWT 由头部（header）、载荷（payload）与签名（signature）组成，一个 JWT 类似下面这样：</p><h3 id="header部分"><a href="#header部分" class="headerlink" title="header部分"></a>header部分</h3><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json">&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;typ&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&quot;JWT&quot;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;alg&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&quot;HS256&quot;</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>alg字段指定了生成signature的算法，默认值为HS256</li><li>typ默认值为JWT<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json">&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;iss&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&quot;http://larabbs.test&quot;</span>, <br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;iat&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-number">1515733500</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;exp&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-number">1515737100</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;nbf&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-number">1515733500</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;jti&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&quot;c3U4VevxG2ZA1qhT&quot;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;sub&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;prv&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&quot;23bd5c8949f600adb39e701c400872db7a5976f7&quot;</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li> <code>sub</code> 面向的用户</li><li> <code>iss</code> JWT的签发者</li><li> <code>iat</code> 签发时间</li><li> <code>exp</code> 过期时间</li><li> <code>nbf</code> 该时间之前不接收处理该token</li><li> <code>jti</code> 该token的唯一标识</li><li>JWT最后使用的是base64进行编码的，也就说不能在这里保存敏感信息*<h2 id="安装Jwt-auth"><a href="#安装Jwt-auth" class="headerlink" title="安装Jwt-auth"></a>安装Jwt-auth</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs composer">composer require tymon/jwt-auth<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>这里为什么不指定版本呢？反正用的是laravel7.x<br>composer会自己给我挑选的<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs php">php artisan jwt:secret<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>生成密钥 会出现在.env中用来jwt-token计算</li></ul><p>接下来去config/auth.php中将guard的driver 改为jwt</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs php"><br><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;guards&#x27;</span> =&gt; [<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;web&#x27;</span> =&gt; [<br>        <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;driver&#x27;</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;session&#x27;</span>,<br>        <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;provider&#x27;</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;users&#x27;</span>,<br>    ],<br><br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;api&#x27;</span> =&gt; [<br>        <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;driver&#x27;</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;jwt&#x27;</span>,<br>        <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;provider&#x27;</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;users&#x27;</span>,<br>    ],<br>],<br> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改 config/api.php，auth 中增加 JWT 相关的配置</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs php"><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;auth&#x27;</span> =&gt; [<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;jwt&#x27;</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Dingo\Api\Auth\Provider\JWT&#x27;</span>,<br>],<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时auth::guard(‘api’)所用的方法就是dingo jwt中的auth了 而 jwt的auth用的是 tymon的jwtauth<br>所以也就是后文中出现了auth::guard(‘api’)-&gt;attempt(用户数据) 后还能放回一个token的原因<br><em>并且我们需要在 users模型中进行继承接口</em><br>App\models\users.php</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs php">.<br>.<br>.<br><span class="hljs-keyword">use</span> <span class="hljs-title">Tymon</span>\<span class="hljs-title">JWTAuth</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Contracts</span>\<span class="hljs-title">JWTSubject</span>;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//新增方法</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//获取当前用户id</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">getJWTIdentifier</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)</span><br><span class="hljs-function">    </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">$this</span>-&gt;getKey();<br>    &#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//用来增加jwt 中的payload</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">getJWTCustomClaims</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)</span><br><span class="hljs-function">    </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> [];<br>    &#125;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们可以使用一下命令为用户生成一个token</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs php">Auth::guard(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;api&#x27;</span>)-&gt;fromUser(<span class="hljs-variable">$user</span>)<br><span class="hljs-comment">//此处的user是用户模型</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="../img/Laravel%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8JWT.asset/image-20211029000305902.png" alt="image-20211029000305902"></p><p>顺便说一句</p><ul><li><code>JWT_TTL</code> 生成的 token 在多少分钟后过期，默认 60 分钟</li><li><code>JWT_REFRESH_TTL</code> 生成的 token，在多少分钟内，可以刷新获取一个新 token，默认 20160 分钟，14 天。</li></ul><p>好了基本的安装就到这里结束了</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
